---
title: Mushroom Gravy-Smothered Striploin Steak  with Roasted Potatoes and Broccolini
description: Fire up the oven and get ready for a perfectly fall-themed steak dinner!  With lemony broccolini, herby mushroom gravy and sirloin seasoned with Montreal Spice Blend, this dinner is full of fresh, autumnal flavours.

